descriptionHTML:
DJ Tiesto watch face for Android Wear smartwatches: Huawei Watch, Sony SmartWatch, Motorola Moto 360, Tag Heuer, Fossil Q, LG G Watch, Asus ZenWatch etc. DJ Tiesto Watch Face for business. Stylish & Elegant. This watchface is compatible with all Android Wear watches. If you are fan of electronic dance music and DJ Tiesto install this Watch Face!

DJ Tiesto Watch Face features:
✔ Support both round and square displays
✔ Watchface for Android Wear watches
✔ 24-hour time format
✔ Battery level
✔ Day of the week
✔ Day of the month

How to use DJ Tiesto Watch Face for Android Wear smartwatches:
1. Once you install the app, the DJ Tiesto watchface will be automatically transferred to your watch. This may take a few minutes. You may have to wait for a while.
2. From smartwatches: Long press your watchface and select the one that you have installed.
From mobile: Run the "Android Wear" app and tap "More" button in the watchface section.
3. Enjoy electronic dance music and your new watchface with DJ Tiesto!
